{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-095-096-tickets-please",
    "title": "Lesson 95: Tickets, please.",
    "audioFilename": "095&096－Tickets, Please..mp3",
    "duration": 97.358,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.69,
      "end": 2.53,
      "text": "Lesson 95.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第95课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 6.65,
      "end": 10.61,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 12.67,
      "end": 16.21,
      "text": "Why did George and Ken miss the train?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "乔治和肯为什么误了火车？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 19.44,
      "end": 22.26,
      "text": "Two return tickets to London, please.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "请给我两张去伦敦的往返票。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 23.56,
      "end": 26.24,
      "text": "What time will the next train leave?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "下一班火车什么时候开？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 27.26,
      "end": 29.74,
      "text": "At nineteen minutes past eight.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "八点十九分。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 30.88,
      "end": 32.34,
      "text": "Which platform?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "在哪个站台？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 34.04,
      "end": 34.54,
      "text": "two.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "2号站台。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 35.12,
      "end": 36.22,
      "text": "Over the bridge.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "过天桥。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 38.22,
      "end": 40.94,
      "text": "What time will the next train leave?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "下一班火车什么时候开？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 42.22,
      "end": 43.76,
      "text": "At eight nineteen.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "八点十九分。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 44.82,
      "end": 47.14,
      "text": "We've got plenty of time.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们时间还很充裕。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 48.52,
      "end": 51.34,
      "text": "It's only three minutes to eight.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "现在才差三分八点。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 52.44,
      "end": 54.66,
      "text": "Let's go and have a drink.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们去喝一杯吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 54.66,
      "end": 59.04,
      "text": "There's a bar next door to the station.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "车站旁边有一家酒吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 60.36,
      "end": 64.4,
      "text": "We had better go back to the station now, Ken.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "肯，我们现在最好回车站去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 66.56,
      "end": 66.84,
      "text": "Tickets, please.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "请出示车票。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 68.26,
      "end": 71.92,
      "text": "We want to catch the eight nineteen to London.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们想赶八点十九分去伦敦的火车。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 72.86,
      "end": 74.9,
      "text": "You've just missed it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你们刚刚错过了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 75.6,
      "end": 76.1,
      "text": "What?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 76.94,
      "end": 79.22,
      "text": "It's only eight fifteen.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "现在才八点十五分。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 79.22,
      "end": 81.7,
      "text": "I'm sorry, sir.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "对不起，先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 82.36,
      "end": 84.88,
      "text": "That clock's ten minutes slow.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那座钟慢了十分钟。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 86.28,
      "end": 87.9,
      "text": "When's the next train?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "下一班火车是什么时候？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "start": 88.84,
      "end": 90.76,
      "text": "In five hours' time.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "五小时以后。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
